OL,3,CConservative MP Craig Mackinlay to
OL,4,Cstand down ahead of General Election
OL,6,FConservative MP Craig Mackinlay, who
OL,7,Fhad his feet and arms amputated after
OL,8,Fdeveloping sepsis, has announced he is
OL,9,Fstanding down ahead of the General
OL,10,FElection.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, the South Thanet MP made
OL,13,Fhis first appearance in the House of
OL,14,FCommons since his sepsis ordeal.
OL,16,FMr Mackinlay was taken to hospital on
OL,17,FSeptember 28 and put into a 16-day
OL,18,Finduced coma, with his wife told he
OL,19,Fhad only a 5% chance of survival.
