OL,3,CConservative MP Craig Mackinlay to
OL,4,Cstand down ahead of General Election
OL,6,FIn a statement to GB News he said:
OL,7,F"Whilst my heart tells me to stand
OL,8,Fagain, there being so much unfinished
OL,9,Fbusiness across local regeneration and
OL,10,Fnational issues which are important to
OL,11,Fme, my head knows this to be
OL,12,Fimpossible at this time.
OL,14,F"It would be difficult to withstand
OL,15,Fthe rigours of an all-out election
OL,16,Fcampaign, a campaign that I'd always
OL,17,Fwish to lead from the front.
