OL,3,CConservative MP Craig Mackinlay to
OL,4,Cstand down ahead of General Election
OL,6,F"Thereafter, upon being re-elected it
OL,7,Fwould be difficult for me to sustain
OL,8,F70 to 80-hour working weeks which were
OL,9,Fthe norm prior to my illness.
OL,11,F"I had hoped to phase my return to the
OL,12,FHouse of Commons over the coming
OL,13,Fmonths as my abilities improved.
OL,15,F"Since leaving in-patient
OL,16,Frehabilitation a month ago my life now
OL,17,Frevolves around various medical
OL,18,Fappointments.
